  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It was a randomized controlled trial conducted at department of Urology, Armed Forces&#xD;
      Institute of Urology, Rawalpindi from 1st January, 2018 July 2019 to 31st March 2021 to&#xD;
      determine the role of oral steroids after Direct Vision Internal Urethrotomy to reduce the&#xD;
      recurrence rate of urethral strictures.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
